<view class="container">
  <view class="card">
    <view class="title">客户登录</view>
    <view class="sub-title">请输入客户 access token，或扫码自动带入 token。</view>

    <view class="field">
      <view class="label">访问 Token</view>
      <input
        class="input"
        placeholder="请输入 token"
        value="{{token}}"
        bindinput="onTokenInput"
      />
    </view>

    <button class="btn-primary" bindtap="onSubmit" loading="{{loading}}" disabled="{{loading}}">
      登录
    </button>
    <button class="btn-plain" bindtap="onScanToken" disabled="{{loading}}">
      扫码登录
    </button>
  </view>

  <view class="card tips">
    <view class="tips-title">调试提示</view>
    <view class="tips-item">1. 先在后端写入 customer.access_token。</view>
    <view class="tips-item">2. 真机调试时把 API 域名改成可访问地址。</view>
    <view class="tips-item">3. 开发者工具可在“本地设置”关闭域名校验做本地联调。</view>
  </view>
</view>
